FBIS4-23376 "drafr108_a_94005" FBIS-AFR-94-108 Daily Report 3 Jun 1994 CENTRAL AFRICA Rwanda RPF Leader Estimates 1 Million Killed in 2 Months RPF Leader Estimates 1 Million Killed in 2 Months EA0306191094 (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura in English to Rwanda 1100 GMT 3 Jun 94 EA0306191094 (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura English BFN [Excerpts] The Rwandan Patriotic Front [RPF] chairman, Colonel Alexis Kanyarengwe, held a press conference yesterday at Mulindi RPF headquarters in northern Rwanda. The press conference was attended by foreign journalists from Italy and Australia. [passage omitted] The RPF chairman condemned the Rwandan leaders for promoting the killings through their preaches, newspapers and government-controlled radios. He estimated the people who have been killed so far in a period of only two months to be close to 1 million.
